{"tid":919642,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV點解唔試下全力做綜藝，唔好再拍劇？","createTime":"2018-11-28T07:57:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T12:45:39.000Z","uid":126769,"like":161,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e8153a33ad91b621ae97082dcc7c342feca4d2","tid":919642,"uid":126769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T07:57:58.000Z","msg":"老實講，如果講拍劇viu一定唔夠tvb鬥，睇之前viu劇收視就知完全唔吸引<br />\n不如試下做多d港產綜藝，請d真係明星做下真人show，唔好貪平搵埋d christylai之流<br />\n之前睇kenny條片就好想香港有呢類綜藝<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fHV0GKm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfHV0GKm.png&h=2bd1ba06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搵堆有綜藝感好笑既藝人明星一齊同居<br />\n香港真係好少笑得出既綜藝<br />\n<br />\n利申:想睇農夫，張繼聰，張敬軒一齊做綜藝，一定笑到仆街"},{"pid":"066f7e04d21b4b876dd941de7ab621480edb21e6","tid":919642,"uid":126769,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T10:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/28/182331_276895cec70bd302bfb4f5f0ac09f0d9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F28%2F182331_276895cec70bd302bfb4f5f0ac09f0d9.png&h=29e87226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢套野如果唔係啲暗星做應該多好多人睇<br />\n好心viu唔好慳呢啲錢"},{"pid":"2875e8d7f3c06caf0daf9c3e8dad7b7760bf1112","tid":919642,"uid":35166,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前就多綜藝先搞成咁，所以先家下拍多返劇再搏一套 有迴響"},{"pid":"3da54a447a34f9c86adac315a11572664d1296d3","tid":919642,"uid":126769,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"2875e8d7f3c06caf0daf9c3e8dad7b7760bf1112","tid":919642,"uid":35166,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之前就多綜藝先搞成咁，所以先家下拍多返劇再搏一套 有迴響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T11:50:47.000Z","msg":"覺得viu做綜藝仲係差啲<br />\n冇咩爆點太平淡<br />\n揀人已經揀錯 搵啲冇綜藝感唔好笑既人做